# Free read-only TMDB (The Movie Database) v3 API key.
# Enables movie title/director autocomplete and posters in the "작품 추가" form.
# Without it the app works exactly as before — autocomplete just stays hidden.
#
# Get one (2 minutes, free): https://www.themoviedb.org/settings/api
# Then copy this file to `.env` and paste your key below.
VITE_TMDB_API_KEY=
